'''[[great]] [[circle]]'''
#A circle defined as the [[intersection]] of the [[surface]] of a [[sphere]] and a [[plane]] which passes through the [[centre]] of the sphere.
#The [[shortest]] [[distance]] between two points on the surface of a sphere.

